file.name: fungenerators.com-lottery-1.5-swagger.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  description: >
    Below is the documentation for the API calls. You can try them out right
    here. 
  title: Random Lottery Number generator
  version: "1.5"
  x-apisguru-categories:
    - entertainment
  x-origin:
    - format: swagger
      url: https://fungenerators.com/yaml/lottery.yaml
      version: "2.0"
  x-providerName: fungenerators.com
  x-serviceName: lottery
tags:
  - description: Random Lottery number generation API
    externalDocs:
      description: Find out more
      url: http://fungenerators.com/api/lottery
    name: Lottery
paths:
  /lottery/countries:
    get:
      description: Get the complete list of countries supported in the number generation
        API.
      responses:
        "200":
          description: 200  response
          content:
            application/json:
              examples:
                response:
                  value: |-
                    { 
                      "success":
                        {"total":76},
                      "contents": {
                         "countries":
                            [
                              "Anguilla",
                              "Antigua and Barbuda",
                              "Australia",
                              "Austria",
                              "..."
                            ]
                      }
                    }
        "401":
          description: 401  response
          content:
            application/json:
              examples:
                response:
                  value: |-
                    {
                        "error": {
                            "code": 401,
                            "message": "Unauthorized"
                        }
                    }
      security:
        - X-Fungenerators-Api-Secret: []
      tags:
        - Lottery
  /lottery/draw:
    get:
      description: Generate random draw for a given lottery game.
      parameters:
        - description: Lottery Game Name
          in: query
          name: game
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            format: string
        - description: Number of draws (max 5 per request)
          in: query
          name: count
          required: false
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: integer
      responses:
        "200":
          description: 200  response
          content:
            application/json:
              examples:
                response:
                  value: |-
                    {
                        "success": {
                            "total": 1
                        },
                        "contents": 
                            {
                              "numbers":
                                [
                                  {"draw":[[21,10,6,44,17,5]]}
                                ]
                            }
                    }
        "401":
          description: 401  response
          content:
            application/json:
              examples:
                response:
                  value: |-
                    {
                        "error": {
                            "code": 401,
                            "message": "Unauthorized"
                        }
                    }
      security:
        - X-Fungenerators-Api-Secret: []
      tags:
        - Lottery
  /lottery/supported:
    get:
      description: Get the list of supported lottery games supported in the given country.
      parameters:
        - description: Country Name
          in: query
          name: country
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            format: string
      responses:
        "200":
          description: 200  response
          content:
            application/json:
              examples:
                response:
                  value: |-
                    {
                        "success": {
                            "total":4
                          
                        },
                        "contents": {
                            "country" : "India",
                            "games" :
                            [
                              "india-playwin-easy-lotto",
                              "india-playwin-fast-digit-lottery",
                              "india-playwin-super-lotto",
                              "india-playwin-thunderball"
                            ]
                        }
                    }            
        "401":
          description: 401  response
          content:
            application/json:
              examples:
                response:
                  value: |-
                    {
                        "error": {
                            "code": 401,
                            "message": "Unauthorized"
                        }
                    }
      security:
        - X-Fungenerators-Api-Secret: []
      tags:
        - Lottery
servers:
  - url: https://api.fungenerators.com
  - url: http://api.fungenerators.com
components:
  securitySchemes:
    X-Fungenerators-Api-Secret:
      in: header
      name: X-Fungenerators-Api-Secret
      type: apiKey
